com.commander4j.db

Class JDBMHNDecisions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBMHNDecisions

  • public class JDBMHNDecisions
extends java.lang.Object
    The JDBMHNDecisions class is used to insert/update/delete records in the table APP_MHN_DECISIONS. This table contains a list of valid decisions which can be applied to the individual pallets which have been assigned to the Master Hold Notice.
